{"tid":1326312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"721 係圍捕 暴力冒警人士？ 還權於民 覺醒世人抗當奴隸","createTime":"2019-07-17T07:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T11:02:39.000Z","uid":143016,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6db4877804510d1d4a122b5226887a9bbfb79fc7","tid":1326312,"uid":143016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:23:13.000Z","msg":"假如捉到落單冒警人士 請記錄容貌 身份 捆綁並集中 一同送回警署<br />\n在警署一字排開 通知記者採訪 並要求警方立案控告 <br />\n<br />\n以下內容由其他post copy <br />\n<br />\n制服冒警人士之前一定要先作出警告<br />\n令所有在場人士，<br />\n甚至睇緊直播人士清楚知道違法者係邊個！<br />\n<br />\n有人冒警！<br />\n你扮警察<br />\n你涉嫌冒警及傷人<br />\n我地行使公民逮捕權<br />\n<br />\n逮捕細節喺呢個post睇：<br />\n你涉嫌冒警及嚴重傷害他人身體，我而家要行使《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條第2項將你拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317207</a>"},{"pid":"a1734c156e7e6feba436d4722f9fa33e7a3a8400","tid":1326312,"uid":143016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"目的是 表達香港市民對冒警及傷人者的身份擔憂<br />\n我地行使公民逮捕權不是為了報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更重要的是推上政治層面 要求香港警察不要對示威者使用過分武力 而不去履行自己職務 逮捕冒警人士"},{"pid":"3c70646df7b0b33f7dcc9e2742f7e91259b80735","tid":1326312,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7vUsxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7vUsxS.png&h=5a5d7319&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b27d29023cbf31f3d34f2a97aeadd6a1dc8955a","tid":1326312,"uid":278386,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"起底<br />\n負評<br />\n封鎖"},{"pid":"6a238352b07bfda27ebdf5c345cb7789cfa891b2","tid":1326312,"uid":16124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5595b0f9c25b39cd06727fc933e760f23719b45d","tid":1326312,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"-文宣-聯署-民意授權-7